   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-converNum-dosPasos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>26: Two groups of 3 is 6, and <m>20+6=26</m>.</li>
      <li>42: I know that <m>4 \times 3</m> is 2 times <m>2 \times 3</m> or <m>2 \times 6</m>, which is 12, and <m>30 + 12 = 42</m>.</li>
      <li>74: I know <m>8 \times 3</m>  is twice <m>4\times 3</m>, so it is <span class="math">\(12+12\)</span>, which is 24. Adding 50 and 24 gives 74.</li>
      <li>123: It's like the one right before it, but you have to add 99 and 24 instead of 50 and 24. Adding 24 to 100 gives 124, so adding 24 to 99 gives 123.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


